The Century of Sex: Playboy's History of the Sexual Revolution, 1900-1999 
by James R. Petersen and Hugh M. Hefner
Grove Press | October 1999 | ISBN-10: 0802116523 | DJVU | 548 pages | 16.3 mb &lt;a href=&quot;
